channel.title: Tornait x Fokkses - High Score Hunter [EDM]
channel.description:
Hey guys, @Fokkses and I just finished a collab. If you like Monstercat-ish stuff, check it out. Even if you're not too fond of Monstercat... Please give us a listen!
https://soundcloud.com/tornait-jaybird/tornait-x-fokkses-high-score
Shoutout to @Fokkses for being so gracious to let me collab with them! This piece was passed back and forth between us— but he came up with the project. Thank you, mate!

item.dc:creator: akabillposters
item.description:
Not my genre - at all - but clearly a really well constructed track with a great central theme. Really good energy and an enjoyable listen.

Funky where it needed to be, fun where it needed to be.

I can imagine this track attracting some attention with a full work-up.

Great work, both of you.
